OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780989356
OL,3,CImages reveal extent of damaged caused
OL,4,Cby Tata Steel fire
OL,6,FA large-scale industrial fire that
OL,7,Fripped through a major processing
OL,8,Fbuilding at the Tata Steel works has
OL,9,Fbeen successfully extinguished.
OL,11,FIt follows a large multi-agency
OL,12,Femergency response lasting more than
OL,13,F48 hours.
OL,15,FMid and West Wales Fire service
OL,16,Fconfirmed that they were called to the
OL,17,Fincident just after 8pm on Wednesday,
OL,18,FJune 3, with crews from 16 local
OL,19,Fstations attending to the blaze.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
