OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,465,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780989356
OL,3,CImages reveal extent of damaged caused
OL,4,Cby Tata Steel fire
OL,6,FThe fire broke out inside an
OL,7,Findustrial structure measuring
OL,8,Fapproximately 1,200 metres by 200
OL,9,Fmetres, housing the site's cold mill
OL,10,Fand pickle line operations.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for the Mid and West
OL,13,FWales Fire and Rescue Service (MAWWFS)
OL,14,Fsaid:
OL,16,F"The fire at the Tata Steel UK Works
OL,17,Fin Port Talbot has now been
OL,18,Fextinguished. Since Wednesday, our
OL,19,Fcrews have dealt with a large-scale
OL,20,Findustrial fire at the steel works.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/4
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
