PN,46403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780989356
OL,3,CImages reveal extent of damaged caused
OL,4,Cby Tata Steel fire
OL,6,F"Overall, with crew rotations, crews
OL,7,Ffrom Port Talbot, Neath, Morriston,
OL,8,FGlynneath, Swansea West, Cymmer,
OL,9,FSwansea Central, Pontarddulais,
OL,10,FLlanelli, Carmarthen, Ammanford,
OL,11,FGorseinon, Pont-iets, Kidwelly,
OL,12,FHaverfordwest, Milford Haven, and
OL,13,FTumble Fire Stations attended the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/4
