PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F464A1780989356
OL,3,CImages reveal extent of damaged caused
OL,4,Cby Tata Steel fire
OL,6,F"With support from South Wales Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service and Avon Fire &
OL,8,FRescue Service, crews responded to a
OL,9,Ffire within an industrial building
OL,10,Fmeasuring approximately 1,200 metres
OL,11,Fby 200 metres, used as a cold mill and
OL,12,Fpickle line.
OL,14,F"Thank you to our Firefighters and our
OL,15,FJoint Control Room Operators for their
OL,16,Fcommitment and hard work!"
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/4
